decision_conditions:
&lt;p&gt;The proposal, by reason of its failure to secure a restriction on new residents being able to apply for parking permits, would be likely to increase parking stress in the area and would fail to promote sustainable forms of
transport. The proposal does not, therefore, fall within the parameters of Class A Part 20 (a) of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted
Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
